column5: What are the dates of teh two Pine Falls Tourneys this year?
voyaguer is oct 6th 7th will check for the other one manitoba .... a 100,000 lakes how many walleyes ???? i will never have enough time....

Did fishing ever get heated up late last year? I fished there early in the first weekend of October and we did pretty well..then if I remember right, weather was not great with lots of wind and cold. I usually make the weekend of the 20th ish but did not make it last year. How about Selkirk? See ya all in a couple weeks! Hawgeye

I was there on Novemeber 13/06. We caught about 10 walleye in the 2-3 lb range but no mamas. Was too windy that day to go out in the bay but I don't think it would have been any better. Indications are that it will be a much better year this year. The plan is to head out on September 15 and try it out. Probably too early but it's a good way to find out. W5
the cwc tourney is friday/saturday oct 12th/13th manitoba .... a 100,000 lakes how many walleyes ???? i will never have enough time....
Anyone know how I can get an application on the web for the first one-Voyageur. ChadM
